{"tid":1146181,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果iPhone XR印度售價大劈22%，幾時輪到香港？","createTime":"2019-05-09T05:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T13:16:10.000Z","uid":213877,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"53ae74d829af6847b14b4898678e60409619b237","tid":1146181,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T05:53:38.000Z","msg":"全球手機市場本周末再起風雲，三星將於4月5日星期五開售全球首款5G手機Galaxy S10 5G，蘋果最新宣布，旗下iPhone XR同日在印度大幅減價最多22%。<br />\n<br />\n印度高端手機市佔率僅排第三<br />\n<br />\n印度《The Economic Times》引述3名業內人士報道，蘋果iPhone XR將於4月5日起下調售價，以刺激銷售。當地市場以中低端手機為主，高端市場競爭激烈，蘋果在高端市場市佔率僅排第3位。<br />\n<br />\n今次3款不同容量的iPhone XR都會減價，減幅為18至22%。上述消息人士稱，蘋果旗艦級手機過去從沒有試過第一年減價，主要是提供現金回贈、免息分期以及換機計劃。"},{"pid":"8eca134a029d1a1c3cdf6126af6070c99d6b4639","tid":1146181,"uid":109923,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T05:56:57.000Z","msg":"寧願買8plus/7plus"},{"pid":"61eb6737819d7cae74dcf1477732fd1f6c759a9a","tid":1146181,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T06:24:34.000Z","msg":"香港實冇份"},{"pid":"e29806faeb01e41f1c11116633044b47d9aa58da","tid":1146181,"uid":98386,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:42:49.000Z","msg":"XR減有撚用 最top嗰部減就話"},{"pid":"3fe7259e76a55b3ce441d5386e3fcc26103186f7","tid":1146181,"uid":3032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:45:37.000Z","msg":"佢地係用oppo 小米 華為<br />\n蘋果太貴"},{"pid":"ed0b32da555fdc6eefdc843b30884c16add4eefe","tid":1146181,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T17:50:40.000Z","msg":"華為好過"},{"pid":"ffef92d3442a8ad1ccdc64f9eb01ebfeb853ac90","tid":1146181,"uid":15835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T20:43:27.000Z","msg":"減完應該真係合理水平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f104831eab4ad58c5827e5870e35b261ec693ab7","tid":1146181,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T